BAPHUTHUNYISWE esibhedlela abafundi nothisha baseVukuzakhe High kwa-M eMlaza kulandela ukuhogela igesi eyingozi ngoMsombuluko. Okhulumela abezimo eziphuthumayo kwaRescue Care, uMnuz Garrith Jamieson uthe babizelwe kule ndawo ukuyosiza abafundi abalinganiselwa ku-60 nothisha ababili okuthiwa bahogele le gesi. "Indiza enophephela emhlane yakwa-Lenmed nabosizo lokuqala babizelwe eMlazi kwa-L lapho abafundi nothisha behogele okusolakala ngokuba igesi enobungozi. Abanye balaba banfundi bebe sesimeni esibucayi ngemuva kokuhogela le gesi. "Kusolakala ukuthi abafanana bakulesi sikole bebedlala ibhola lase liyasikeka nokuyilapho kuphume khona igesi. Ezinye zeziguli zihlengelwe endaweni yesigameko ngaphambi kokuphuthunyiswa ezibhedlela ezahlukene zaseThekwini," kusho uJamieson. "Oyedwa obelimele kakhulu uthathwe yindiza enophephela emhlane waphuthunyiswa eLenmed eThekwini Hospital okuyilapho athola khona ukwelashwa, kanti abanye basemtholampilo kwa-L eMlaza. Okwamanje akukaziwa ukuthi hlobo luni lwegesi abayihogelile," kuchaza uJamieson. Amaphoyisa nabeziqhumane kanye nabeSearch and Rescue bebesendaweni yesigameko ukuzophenya. Abafundi balesi sikole bathunyelwe emakhaya isikole savalwa. 